### Code Blocks

```javascript
// Example JavaScript code with syntax highlighting
function greet(name) {
  const message = `Hello, ${name}!`;
  console.log(message);
  return message;
}

// Call the function
greet("Curtains");
```

```python
# Python example
def fibonacci(n):
    """Generate Fibonacci sequence up to n"""
    a, b = 0, 1
    while a < n:
        print(a, end=' ')
        a, b = b, a + b
    print()

fibonacci(100)
```

